latestPosts.caption:
Sasson – One of My Favorite Spots in Pune!🌸🌙

If you’re a true foodie and love capturing Instagram-worthy moments, Sasson is a must-visit. This place has the perfect mix of cozy vibes, aesthetic interiors, and mouthwatering food that looks just as good as it tastes.

From their perfectly curated dishes to the absolutely crazy good boba tea (which they’ve recently launched and it’s a total game-changer!), everything here is crafted with detail and love. Whether you’re out for a chill evening or looking for your next content-worthy café, Sasson hits all the right notes.🥰🌈

Highly recommend this gem for all food and boba lovers in Pune!❤️💃

📸 @pankaj_kurmi46
